  characterName: Fiat Panda (1st generation)
  characterPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 31721af7b265fac4fa93e891e3387e8b, type: 3}
  lines:
  - Some people say the Fiat Panda (1st generation) looks like a 'box on wheels'.
  - But daddy Giorgetto Giugiaro made no mistakes with me.
  - Gweenith can't get enough of these pressed steel body panels.
  - This cast iron engine.
  - This Aluminium cylinder head.
  - I make Gweenith wet.
  - Which is something you have failed to do for the past 14 years.
  - Cuck.
  textSpeed: 30
  typingSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: f5d143911732a1f43b570748ed2458a4, type: 3}
